*Digital Bookshelf*
Create: Add a new book with its title, author, and page count.
Read: Filter books by a specific author or genres.
Update: Change the status from "Reading" to "Finished".
Delete: Remove a book you no longer own.


mysql>  CREATE TABLE BOOKS(
    ->  Book_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ->  Title VARCHAR(50),
    ->  Author VARCHAR(50),
    ->  Genre VARCHAR(50),
    ->  Page_count INT,
    -> status VARCHAR(20)
    -> );
